headline: CAH Q3 Deep Dive: Specialty Expansion, M&A Drive Strong Top-Line Growth
summary: Healthcare distributor and services company Cardinal Health (NYSE:CAH) reported Q3 CY2025 results topping the market’s revenue expectations, with sales up 22.4% year on year to $64.01 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $2.55 per share was 17.3% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
